cruise_purpose:
The objectives are to: 
1)        Test, calibrate, and evaluate the deep-towed Deep-See acoustical and optical system;
2)        Collect acoustical and optical data on deep-scattering layers using Deep-See and EK60; 
3)        Sample plankton and nekton using MOCNESS nets and midwater trawls; 
4)        Collect hydrographic and meteorological data; 
5)        Collect eDNA samples;
6)        Characterize surface layer plankton communities (IFCB) and associated productivity (EIMS); and
7)        Document the scientific activities using photos, videos, and interviews.

